A collection of assorted categories to common Cocoa Touch classes


 * UIColor+ColorFromString

   Adds a class method to UIColor for creating UIColor objects from a string

   + (UIColor *)colorFromString:(NSString *)string;
   Class method that returns a color object based on the RGBA components
   specified as a comma-separated string of decimal (0.0 to 1.0) values, 
   eg. @"0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 1.0" for 100% opaque gray


 * UITextView+RoundedCorners

   Adds an instance method to UITextView to toggle rounded corners appearance

   - (void)setRoundedCorners:(BOOL)rounded;
   Instance method to specify if the receiver should draw itself with rounded
   corners and a border


